NIPAH VIRUS, PIGS - MALAYSIA (11)
*********************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed/html>
See Also
Nipah virus, pigs - Malaysia (07) 990502033808
Nipah virus, pigs - Malaysia (07): CORRECTION 990505180824
